name: Symphony of day and night 🌚 🌝  OE + AR

metadata.name: Symphony of day and night 🌚 🌝  OE + AR
metadata.description:
Meet the first open edition by Napasio
This artwork was exhibited in New York, Dubai and Almaty.
The work is accompanied by an AR mask that completes the picture with animation (in Napasio`s ig profile)

In the magical art universe Napasio World, like nowhere else, you can see that black and white, day and night, good and evil are not only irreconcilable opposites, but also parts of one whole. Everything is one.
